headline: Investing around market complacency even as volatility falls off
summary: While market volatility (^VIX) draws down from April highs, Explosive Options Technical Analyst Bob Lang comes on Market Domination Overtime to comment on the shift in investor sentiment even as stocks (^DJI, ^IXIC, ^GSPC) rallied this week on the headlines of US-China trade talks. Lang weighs in on how to invest around market complacency. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime here.

headline: Week’s Best: Fidelity Has Login Problems
summary: Fidelity’s website experienced technical problems on Monday morning, and some customers were unable to gain access to their accounts as stocks rallied on news that the U.S. and China were enacting a partial pause on some tariffs.  Financial advisors can increase their value by making sure clients spend their money and time on things that make them feel happy and fulfilled, writes columnist Brian Parker, founder of EP Wealth Advisors.  Crafting a solid financial plan and making sure clients won’t run out of money may not be enough to provide them with true peace of mind.
